## **Which Links to Use:**

General links work on all devices &amp; Facebook. 

Web links work only on computers via the Bingo Blitz web platform.

VIP Web links work only on computers for VIP Pro users. 

____________ 
## **How &amp; Where to Collect &amp; Info:**

Ensure you are logged into the correct account before clicking any links (especially if using **Sign in with Apple**). 

If not signed in, log in and then click the link again. 

To change accounts after collecting, log out via game menu &gt; Connect/Logout &gt; Logout, then sign into your desired account. You may need to cache clear too.

All links are active at posting; expiration times are in UTC - convert to your local time here: [[[[[https://www.timeanddate.com/time/difference/timezone/utc](https://www.timeanddate.com/time/difference/timezone/utc)](https://www.timeanddate.com/time/difference/timezone/utc)](https://www.timeanddate.com/time/difference/timezone/utc)](https://www.timeanddate.com/time/difference/timezone/utc)](https://www.timeanddate.com/time/difference/timezone/utc)

Fan Page Stories &amp; Instagram Stories incentives may expire after 24 hours. 

**Already collected** means an incentive can only be claimed once (except those marked with <span class="html-span xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xm2jcoa x1mpyi22 xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od"><img height="16" width="16" class="xz74otr x15mokao x1ga7v0g x16uus16 xbiv7yw" alt="🔁" referrerpolicy="origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/te/1/16/1f501.png"></span>: 5 Daily Credits [♳] every 24 hours, 2 Three-Day Gifts [♵] every 72 hours, 4 Team Gifts [♹] every 168 hours). 

**Not eligible** appears if an incentive is for a specific group (e.g. Bingo Blitz PLUS requires an active PLUS subscription).

Exclusive Gifts (marked <span class="html-span xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1hl2dhg x16tdsg8 x1vvkbs x3nfvp2 x1j61x8r x1fcty0u xdj266r xat24cr xm2jcoa x1mpyi22 xxymvpz xlup9mm x1kky2od"><img height="16" width="16" class="xz74otr x15mokao x1ga7v0g x16uus16 xbiv7yw" alt="🌍" referrerpolicy="origin-when-cross-origin" src="https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t3f/1/16/1f30d.png"></span>) are BBGC‑exclusive and must not be shared outside our private group. 

Free Rounds aren’t posted here – check your personal emails or notifications.

____________ 
# **Promo Codes:**

Promo codes are occasionally published on Bingo Blitz social media and do NOT replace freebie links. 

We only share officially published, working promo codes. Please do not post unofficial codes.
